A cyberpunk-style digital interface floating in a neon-lit void, showing a sleek holographic dashboard with multiple translucent data streams flowing like rivers of glowing cyan and magenta particles. A disembodied hand wearing a futuristic glove reaches toward the streams, fingers positioned to drag and redirect the flowing data into different organizational channels that branch off like neural pathways. The streams contain abstract geometric shapes representing different content types—cubes, spheres, pyramids—all pulsing with inner light. The background features dark chrome surfaces with circuit-like patterns etched in electric blue, rain droplets catching neon reflections. The overall mood suggests empowerment and control over digital chaos, with a sense of fluid reorganization and purposeful action.
